com.incadencecorp.coalesce.framework

Class EnumerationProviderUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.incadencecorp.coalesce.framework.EnumerationProviderUtil

  • public final class EnumerationProviderUtil
extends Object
    This utility class allows for multiple implementations of IEnumerationProvider to be used for defining enumerations used by the CoalesceEnumerationField. If this utility is not initialized before using it will call initializeFromConnector().
    Author:
    n78554
